description: Bright and spacious, this two-bedroom plus a spacious office with great light and large windows, two-bathroom penthouse with parking is perfectly situated on the east side of South Boston! Offering an ideal layout, this sun-drenched residence boasts private outdoor space and abundant storage, including a convenient entryway/mudroom. The third-floor home features an inviting eat-in kitchen with a new gas range, brand-new in-unit laundry, a private deck, and dedicated basement storage. Located in a pet-friendly, self-managed building, it’s just a short walk to the beach, South Boston’s top restaurants, and major highways
